.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, pop, metal, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the fan rock##1
2. the fan r&b is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the fan metal is the fan metal##1
6. the fan metal is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the fan metal is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5
8. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | pop | metal    | rock  | r&b   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

