2. the fan gospel is not the person traveling to prague##6
3. the person traveling to london is the fan d&b##1
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
5. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the fan country##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | new-york | prague     | marseilles | london |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | reggae      | d&b         |

