2. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the mexican is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the argentine is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the argentine##3
6. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking milk is not the mexican##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | milk  | 7up        | soy-milk      | tea          |
| Job        | indonesian | argentine | mexican | brazilian |

