.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, lawyer, teacher
City: marseilles, prague, paris, hannover
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is not the teacher##6
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is the lawyer##1
7. the bartender is not the person traveling to hannover##6
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bartender  | lawyer | teacher    | fisherman |
| Transport   | prague | hannover | paris | marseilles  |

