.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bus, van, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person driving the trike##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person driving the trike##6
6. the person driving the bus is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | scooter     | trike | bus | van |

