3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
